com.konakartadmin.utils
Class ResetDatabase

java.lang.Object
  com.konakartadmin.utils.ResetDatabase

public class ResetDatabase
extends java.lang.Object

Reset the database - this removes all the data in a KonaKart system other than that required to start loading new data once again.

Data that IS removed:

  • Products
  • Options
  • Custom Attributes
  • Manufacturers
  • Categories
  • Bookings
  • Subscriptions
  • Promotions
  • Miscellaneous Items
  • Expressions
  • Orders
  • Wish Lists
  • Audit Data
Data that isn't removed:
  • Customers
  • Languages
  • Countries
  • Tax
  • Zones, Tax Zones, Geo Zones
  • Currencies
  • Configurations
  • Internal Data such as Panels, Roles, APIs etc
